<br>
The items that you can acquire with sufficient AP are of vex thal and beyond quality. Let's leave out any comparison in difficulty and just use that term to get an idea of what kind of items we're talking about quality wise.<br>
<br>
Right now these items can be acquired by a long string of relatively trivial encounters. It's both a huge timesink (bad), and of low difficulty (bad). I'd rather have tiers of items that can be acquired through tiered missions (easyl-medium-hard) where you get quality of loot that reflect the difficulty of (single group) encounters.<br>
<br>
