16/19 +9% backstab dagger (14/19 +2 dmg aug), with a proc of your choice, and some other stats.<br>
Chain tunic: AC: 61 Str: +13, Dex: +11, Wis: +10, HP +100, Mana +100 Sv Fire: +12, Sv Cold: +12, Sv Poison: +12 Rec. level: 65 type2, type2, type 3 (so add aob/veng 3, and 40-45 hps, and say, +5 all resists).<br>
